Cell["\<\
There does not seem to be a strong relationship between any of the \
independent variable, which the correlation matrix also confirms. There is \
also no sign of a non-linear relationship between an independent variable and \
the dependent variable.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.86800843628434*^9, 
  3.868008510034809*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6e465b94-b80b-4241-801d-\
10ebb30fee52"],

Cell["\<\
Unfortunately there also does not seem to be a relationship between most of \
the explanatory variables and the dependent variable.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.86800843628434*^9, 
  3.868008545246767*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"242d364a-9256-48fe-85d2-\
0aaa18ca2f79"]
}, Open  ]],

