Cell["\<\
In contrast to the same plot in the cross-sectional analysis, there is no \
pattern. Thus, it is safe to assume, there is no heteroskedasticity and a \
similar transformation to the one in the cross-sectional analysis is not \
necessary.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.868008585498918*^9, 
  3.868008689217188*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"19eadd9f-cf5e-415d-8adc-\
9c43f09827d7"]
}, Open  ]],

