Cell["\<\
At a 5% level, we can not conclude skewness and excess kurtosis to be 0.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.868008960610292*^9, 3.8680089700826263`*^9}, {
  3.868009022238064*^9, 3.868009038792515*^9}, {3.868012144454526*^9, 
  3.868012144455503*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d24c97eb-b872-4e41-b0e5-\
e4fb4262884e"],

Cell["\<\
Since, according to my notes of the statistics class regarding linear \
regression models, this is not an issue except for prediction bands, this is \
not  address this (since calculating prediction bands is not part of the \
analysis).\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.868008960610292*^9, 3.8680089700826263`*^9}, {
  3.868009022238064*^9, 3.868009038792515*^9}, {3.868012145357936*^9, 
