Cell["\<\
Even though we are dealing with a time-series, the timeplot of the residuals \
does not indicate the residuals to be correlated with each other.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.86801054461357*^9, 
  3.8680105971578903`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2a022fb2-c749-40b0-84b9-\
ae68aa7fdda9"],

Cell["\<\
The Durbin-Watson test confirms that: A value between 1.5 and 2.5 means  \
autocorrelation to a problematic degree is not present.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.86801054461357*^9, 3.868010641882667*^9}, {
  3.868012852213812*^9, 
  3.868012862929034*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1a5d6493-dbfb-4e12-be56-\
ea3bfbafda02"]
}, Open  ]],

